CustomField.formula: IF(ISPICKVAL(Overall_Satisfaction_for_TCM__c, 'Very Dissatisfied') , 1, IF( ISPICKVAL(Overall_Satisfaction_for_TCM__c, 'Somewhat Dissatisfied') , 2, IF( ISPICKVAL(Overall_Satisfaction_for_TCM__c, 'Neither satisfied nor dissatisfied'), 3, IF( ISPICKVAL(Overall_Satisfaction_for_TCM__c, 'Somewhat satisfied'), 4, IF( ISPICKVAL(Overall_Satisfaction_for_TCM__c, 'Very satisfied'), 5, null)))))
CustomField.label: Overall Satisfaction for TCM
